  "original_title": "\u0b95.\u0baa\u0bca.\u0ba4. \u0b89\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb0 \u0baa\u0bb0\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1  - \u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "G.P.D. Postponement of Higher Level Examinations - Ministry of Education",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Education Minister Sushil Prema Jayantha has said that the General Standard High Level Examinations have been postponed by one month.",
        "He further said that the results of the high-level examination for the year 2021 will be published on August 15."
      ],
